  "texts": [
    "Because U-Net has an encoder-decoder structure with skip connections, contextual information can thereby be modelled along with preserved spatial localization.",
    "While the encoder extracts the features of multiple levels of abstraction, the decoder reconstructs the segmented image with great detail in delineating the cancerous sections.",
    "Further, skip connections connect the gap between the encoder and decoder, preserving the lost spatial information during the process of down sampling.",
    "This architecture by U-Net makes it especially suitable for segmenting colorectal cancer tissues, reflected in the high IoU score of 0.93 realized in this work.",
    "These coupled components form a hybrid model, the PolynetDWTCADx framework, which has both classification and segmentation purposes."
  ],
